<Content>Not what you would expect of a luxury hotel We stayed here for our tenth anniversary. Luckily our trip to Boston did not hinge on the satisfaction of our hotel as we spent very little time there. However, having stayed in many luxury hotels in the world, I would say that this one did not qualify. For one thing, the sheets were substandard. At this price I expect smooth white sheets - high thread count and all, including that I shouldn't even have to mention, fitted bottom sheets. At this hotel, the sheets were the kind that feel kind of textured - yuck. I even asked to see another room to compare, in case ours was atypical. It was typical. And, they do not have fitted sheets. So, the bottom sheet crumples up on you and it equates to a less than comfortable nights sleep. The beds were too low. No pillow top here. We were in a re-decorated room. Oops, the designer didn't take function into consideration when the fancy valance box drape over the bed completely cut out the reading light. The bathroom had a leaky toilet and a cheap thin plastic toilet seat and the door did not open 90 degrees and hit the nightstand. There were no deep drawers in the bedroom. Only thin narrow ones big enough for underwear or sox. Three sets of those but no deep drawers. There was a red substance (blood?) on the wall that I had to ask to be cleaned off, during the first hour when I complained about a stain on the sheets and asked that the entire bed, including mattress pad be remade. During that same visit by the housekeeping staff I asked that they dust all surfaces as every glass surface was thick with dust, to which a rediculous excuse was made. I was disgusted that when we returned from our day, they did not do this and I had to ask again at the front desk. The staff was NOT apologetic but made excuses instead. Later that night, we ordered a drink from room service which never arrived and we had to call asking about it, were put on hold, gave up, and had to call again! We were given the excuse that they were very busy that night. Infuriated, we cancelled the drink. All in all, I would never stay at this hotel again. The price is way too high for the condition of the room and the lack of service. 
